{"tid":2200337,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武肺百死同日 港府謝中央","createTime":"2020-09-13T01:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T02:59:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5bd376447c427c7b54de67c079f8af5a134361","tid":2200337,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/H3AN6K7INVB3PKGEFIFBGJRL7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FH3AN6K7INVB3PKGEFIFBGJRL7M%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513XdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=c053a1d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FH3AN6K7INVB3PKGEFIFBGJRL7M%2F&h=9324daea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/H3AN6K7INVB3PKGEFIFBGJRL7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n武肺百死同日 港府謝中央<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nS91NGispIG_LgTOYZGBl918M2g=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GYOEFJH3JNCWRGQE4KVDSK7CPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnS91NGispIG_LgTOYZGBl918M2g%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGYOEFJH3JNCWRGQE4KVDSK7CPE.jpg&h=766d85b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■第100名死者居深水埗普陞閣，其妻相信上月亦已病故。許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n【疫禍傷逝】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：伴妻丘伯不治 玻璃傳情令人動容<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】她自覺沒有殺人，百人卻為她而死。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n一名67歲有長期病患的男病人。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：病情急速惡化 兩人入院即日亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/up5pLlSF0Yr9yh13IOtwiNI_RfM=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AH3WP6FE4VEV5JRGUAAFCEMNLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fup5pLlSF0Yr9yh13IOtwiNI_RfM%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAH3WP6FE4VEV5JRGUAAFCEMNLY.jpg&h=307cb6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政務司長張建宗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放寬入境檢疫掀第三波爆發<br />\n<br />\n根據衞生防護中心資料，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本港疫潮的首五個月，面對源自中國和海外的第一波和第二波爆發，超過1,200個確診者中，只有七人不幸離世，死亡率僅0.56%，遠較全球死亡率約3.2%低。然而，政府其後以經濟及人道理由，放寬入境人士檢疫措施，製造缺口，引爆嚴重的第三波疫潮，死亡率增至超過2.5%。<br />\n<br />\n香港曾一度錄得連續21日本地零確診紀錄，但7月5日終於斷纜，第三波爆發自此揭開序幕。多名專家指出政府的豁免檢疫政策很可能是源頭，特別是6月8日進一步放寬入境人士檢疫措施，為病毒大開中門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Huvaj0z8Xs85nv1J0wC65n22qtI=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YBKSL24LCNE3NMY2GTSCAANF7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHuvaj0z8Xs85nv1J0wC65n22qtI%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYBKSL24LCNE3NMY2GTSCAANF7Y.jpg&h=6d878af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港府豁免海員檢疫，被指是導致第三波爆發的源頭。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病人組織倡獨立調查問責<br />\n<br />\n香港醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明大罵政府不聽民意，導致第三波爆發和死亡人數急升至百人，「（政府）一開始就唔聽民意，唔了解醫護咁嚴峻都要罷工明志，就係驚武肺爆發，重蹈沙士覆轍 。」她批評政府在疫症爆發至今七個多月，仍不封關，「船員將病毒帶入香港，社區大規模爆發，呢個係政府責任。」她亦不滿政府從未為人命損失問責，「冇歉意，唔覺自己有責任，記者問啲官員會唔會道歉或負責任，（官員）一直迴避問題，唔肯承擔責任。」<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒亦指，本港失去百條人命，「責任一定喺政府度，源頭係豁免檢疫，短期內有一大批人豁免檢疫」，抗疫的督導委員會暨指揮中心由林鄭月娥親自領導，「一定要負責，尤其好多決定由佢話事。」<br />\n<br />\n關注病人權益的社區組織協會幹。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0be6b25f5613d4bd50f1cc2955e729d542daf880","tid":2200337,"uid":136797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:58:29.000Z","msg":"不解釋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGDLMt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGDLMt7.jpg&h=22a60e7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea271a41296d31fe88db24ae596d287e1c9118a2","tid":2200337,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRoWTtm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRoWTtm.jpg&h=5a52f3cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3f55feb6cd1f60f0c72f499ce39efb53f14f6b0","tid":2200337,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea271a41296d31fe88db24ae596d287e1c9118a2","tid":2200337,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRoWTtm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRoWTtm.jpg&h=5a52f3cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"呢張相正<br />\n苛政猛於虎 好多港豬仲FF可以得一枕安夕"}]}